    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;illusion&nbsp;(shadow)&nbsp;[shadow];\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;shaman 9, sorcerer/wizard 9, witch 9;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    \n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;see text<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;see text<br>\n    <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;Will disbelief (if interacted with); varies; see text;&nbsp;<strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>This spell functions like <i>shadow transmutation</i>, except it can mimic <i>greater <i>polymorph</i></i> instead of <i>polymorph</i>. The illusory attacks and special abilities of any shape assumed using greater <i>shadow transmutation</i> deal three-fifths (60%) damage to nonbelievers, and nondamaging effects are 60% likely to work against nonbelievers.</p>\n</div>\n",
